---
const SITE_NAME = "The-Circle";
const DISCORD_INVITE = "https://discord.gg/9rPcHQZ7SH";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>About • {SITE_NAME}</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/svg+xml">
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="What The-Circle is, why it exists, and what we're building."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <header class="top">
        <div class="container nav">
          <a class="brand" href="/">
            <img class="mark" src="/favicon.png" alt="The-Circle" />
            <span>{SITE_NAME}</span>
          </a>
          <nav class="links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/discord">Discord</a>
            <a href="/league">League</a>
            <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="container">
        <section class="card">
          <div class="head">
            <h1>About {SITE_NAME}</h1>
          </div>

          <p class="lead">
            The-Circle is a collection of community projects created and run by TGS.
            The goal is simple: build fun, useful, chill things that people can enjoy together online.
          </p>

          <p class="text">
            Some projects are social, some are game-related, and some are just ideas that felt worth building.
            Everything here is meant to be easy to use, kept clean, and built for real people — not engagement farming.
          </p>

          <div class="callout">
            <h2>The deal</h2>
            <div class="pills">
              <span class="pill2">Free</span>
              <span class="pill2">No ads</span>
              <span class="pill2">No memberships</span>
              <span class="pill2">No weird catch</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text">
              If something ever stops being fun or useful, it gets fixed or replaced. That’s the whole point.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid">
            <div class="tile">
              <h2>What’s here right now</h2>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>The-Circle Discord</strong> — hang out, talk, game, watch stuff, chill in voice.</li>
                <li><strong>The-Circle League</strong> — a private fantasy football league hub with history, teams, and rules.</li>
                <li><strong>More projects</strong> — coming as the site grows.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="tile">
              <h2>What The-Circle isn’t</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>Not a clout server</li>
                <li>Not a product promo hub</li>
                <li>Not a dating server</li>
                <li>Not a drama pit</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2>Where to start</h2>
          <p class="text">
            Most people start with the Discord if they want a place to hang out and meet people.
            The League hub is mainly for the fantasy league itself.
          </p>

          <div class="cta">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/discord">Discord page</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/league">League hub</a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
          </div>

          <p class="fine">
            This site is actively being built. Updates usually get posted in the blog.
          </p>
        </section>
      </main>

      <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container foot">
          <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE_NAME}</span>
          <span class="muted">About The-Circle</span>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <style is:global>
      html, body { height: 100%; }

      body{
        margin:0;
        min-height:100vh;
        font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;
        color:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);

        background-image:
          radial-gradient(900px 500px at 15% 10%, rgba(9,255,3,0.14), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(800px 450px at 85% 15%, rgba(120,170,255,0.18), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(700px 450px at 55% 95%, rgba(255,170,120,0.10), transparent 55%),
          linear-gradient(#070a0f, #070a0f);

        background-repeat:no-repeat;
        background-size:100% 100%;
        background-attachment:fixed;
      }

      .page{ min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
      main{ flex:1; }

      a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
      .container{ max-width:1020px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 18px; }

      .top{
        position:sticky;
        top:0;
        z-index:10;
        backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
        background:rgba(7,10,15,0.55);
        border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      }

      .nav{
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:space-between;
        padding:14px 18px;
        gap:14px;
      }

      .brand{
        display:flex;
        gap:10px;
        align-items:center;
        font-weight:800;
        letter-spacing:-0.02em;
        white-space:nowrap;
      }

      .mark{width:28px;height:28px;display:block;flex:0 0 28px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:0; /* important: don't force a dot */background:transparent;box-shadow:none;filter: drop-shadow(0 6px 16px rgba(9,255,3,0.25));}

      .links{ display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:center; }
      .links a{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.78); font-size:14px; }
      .links a:hover{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.95); }

      .card{
        margin:28px 0;
        border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        border-radius:18px;
        padding:20px;
        box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      }

      .head{ display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; }

      h1{ margin:0 0 10px; font-size:34px; letter-spacing:-0.02em; }
      h2{ margin:18px 0 8px; font-size:18px; }

      .lead{
        color:rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
        font-size:17px;
        line-height:1.6;
        max-width:86ch;
        margin:0 0 10px;
      }

      .text{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72); line-height:1.7; max-width:92ch; }

      .callout{
        margin-top:14px;
        border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius:16px;
        padding:16px;
        background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      .pills{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-top:8px; }
      .pill2{
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        padding:8px 10px;
        border-radius:999px;
        border:1px solid rgba(9,255,3,0.20);
        background:rgba(9,255,3,0.08);
        color:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
        font-size:12px;
      }

      .grid{
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));
        gap:12px;
        margin-top:14px;
      }

      .tile{
        border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        border-radius:16px;
        padding:16px;
        background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      }

      ul{ margin:8px 0 0 18px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72); line-height:1.65; }

      .cta{
        display:flex;
        gap:12px;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        margin-top:16px;
      }

      .btn{
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:center;
        padding:12px 16px;
        border-radius:14px;
        border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
        background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
        transition:transform .12s ease, background .12s ease;
      }

      .btn:hover{ transform:translateY(-1px); background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }
      .btn.primary{ border-color:rgba(9,255,3,0.22); background:rgba(9,255,3,0.10); }
      .btn.ghost{ background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }

      .fine{ margin-top:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size:13px; }

      .footer{
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
        background: rgba(7,10,15,0.35);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .foot{
        display:flex;
        justify-content:space-between;
        gap:12px;
        padding:16px 18px;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
      }

      .muted{ color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }

      @media (max-width:820px){
        .links{ display:none; }
        .grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
